# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the five permanent members of the un security council held unscheduled consultations here thursday on a binding franco-british draft resolution demanding a halt to iran 's uranium enrichment .
# ::alignments
(h / hold-04
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :quant 5
            :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (o / organization
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Un"
                              :op2 "Security"
                              :op3 "Council"))
                  :ARG2 (m / member
                        :mod (p2 / permanent))))
      :ARG1 (c / consult-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG2 (r / resolution
                  :ARG1-of (d / draft-01)
                  :ARG0-of (b / binding-07)
                  :ARG0-of (d2 / demand-01
                        :ARG1 (h3 / halt-01
                              :ARG1 (e / enrich-01
                                    :ARG0 (c2 / country
                                          :name (n2 / name
                                                :op1 "Iran"))
                                    :ARG1 (u / uranium))))
                  :mod (c3 / country
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "France")))
            :ARG1-of (s / schedule-01
                  :polarity -))
      :location (h4 / here)
      :time (d3 / date-entity
            :weekday (t / thursday)))

                        :op1 "Somalia"))
            :mod (f / final))

      :time (w / wednesday)
      :ARG1-of (c2 / cause-01
            :ARG0 (a / and
                  :op1 (m2 / mass-01
                        :ARG1 (f2 / force
                              :ARG2-of (t2 / task-01)
                              :ARG1-of (l / lead-02
                                    :ARG0 o))
                        :location (o2 / off
                              :op1 (c3 / city
                                    :name (n3 / name
                                          :op1 "Mugadishu"))))

                              :quant 2
                              :ARG0-of l
                              :ARG1 (f3 / faction))
                        :ARG1-of (k / key-02))

                        :polarity -
                        :ARG0 p3
                        :ARG1 p)
                  :ARG1-of (r / renew-01))))

                                    :quant 1

            :ARG1-of (s / serious-02))
      :time (w / wednesday)

            :ARG0 o

                  :domain (s2 / start-01

# ::id 1901 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

            :op1 (p / person
                  :name (n / name

                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Ron"
                        :op2 "Shelton")
                  :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG2 (d / director
                              :ARG0-of (w / write-01))))
            :ARG0-of (p3 / partner-01
                  :ARG1 (c / comedy
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Bull"
                              :op2 "Durham")
                        :mod (b / baseball)
                        :ARG1-of (r / rate-01
                              :ARG2 1))))
      :ARG1 (j / jaunt-00
            :ARG1 (w2 / world
                  :mod (g / golf))
            :ARG1-of (r2 / resemble-01)))
